    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到 谜样传说</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部沉浸式心理惊悚选集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您正在体验本系列的第部作品 《谜样传说：十字路口》，预计游戏时间约为2小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/91ac18745ada61839c3e220c06dd1d8a.poster.avif?t=1769058294\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/91ac18745ada61839c3e220c06dd1d8a.webm?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/91ac18745ada61839c3e220c06dd1d8a.mp4?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乔恩是一位来自上世纪90年代的有才华的音乐人，他正努力过上自己最好的生活。 在和女友分手后，乔恩已经在公寓里闷了几个星期，只是不断看电视。 但他的旧工作传呼机却突然开始响起，向他发送神秘的信息，好像……有人在跟踪他。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a210184e70515eea12cd1c89c898a5b8.poster.avif?t=1769058294\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a210184e70515eea12cd1c89c898a5b8.webm?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a210184e70515eea12cd1c89c898a5b8.mp4?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某个人，或某种东西正在跟踪乔恩，一个跟踪者。是谁在发送这些神秘的信息？他们想要什么？为什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a033118d8e4ad7927ea2f45d9de3a675.poster.avif?t=1769058294\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a033118d8e4ad7927ea2f45d9de3a675.webm?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120510/extras/a033118d8e4ad7927ea2f45d9de3a675.mp4?t=1769058294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在乔恩公寓里嗡鸣般的寂静中徘徊。 尝试重拾日常。 冲一杯咖啡。 看动画片。 做家务。 在短暂的安逸中好好享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式且令人不安的叙事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富有氛围感的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高质量的画面与音效</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90年代的怀旧美学</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温馨的公寓生活与模拟元素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接收来自NPC的传呼机消息</p></li></ul>",
